{"id": "1500482159499284552", "channel_id": "1500392202856038470", "author_id": "250664395749720065", "author_name": "_pdt", "content": "Pretty much any Derived card lacks the section in the SS that shows where it gets multipliers.\n(Jenkin's \"Swarm Impact\" is the only exception I've found so far)\nSome other effects are hidden or lack description:\n\n-E3 Karen's Marvelous Cousine gains 50% chance to trigger \"Marvelous Effects\" (?)\n-Tinct Rouse grants: Random Effects (?)\n-Corposant's Pilot shows how much Shield and STR but not the multipliers.\n-Doresain (haven't really used him, but I guess that \"Evernight Revel\" doesn't have a proper description/multipliers)\n-Pollux (Don't have him, but I guess that Sacred Heart also doesn't have the multipliers).\n-Castor's Plume shows final Shield result, but not multipliers.\n-Tawil 2/4/6 wings lack multipliers, 4/6 also lack description.\n-Daffodil Exalt cards are just hidden.\n\nAnd like OP said, we probably have more...", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:00:24.435000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500392202856038470", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-03T17:18:16.661000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1500482159213805579", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1082479, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500392202856038470/1500482159213805579/image.png?ex=69f89868&is=69f746e8&hm=1cc351e393f34fe37af11c9da362d68cd8e7e1a11aefb7a10d4f77e250953d99&"}]}
